{"tid":1207324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[贊成正皮,Thx！]香港人Value：人少暴動，人多就係運動！！！","createTime":"2019-06-12T06:02:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T06:06:21.000Z","uid":61280,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9cc0414d0fc8c4143b77ba10b45041f5017930ed","tid":1207324,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:02:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">眾志成城，利己利人！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"f5497cc71c00a3dbfe61e23f736dce1bbf6eadbf","tid":1207324,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:03:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"948dd73d41653d1dcb032ced79296135663680d1","tid":1207324,"uid":4739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:06:21.000Z","msg":"有人用棍拍野deam beat 既時候唔好劣<br />\n一齊叫同一句口號加士氣避免士氣此消彼長<br />\n有心理學背後原理<br />\n對陣口號可參考港隊打氣口號<br />\n拍拍~拍拍拍~DIE FOR HONG KONG<br />\n<br />\n引用 雞肉大師 巴打:<br />\n要佢哋一齊嘶哮， 進入同一個呼吸節奏 同一個心跳步伐 <br />\n配合戰鼓(你搵個大水樽好撚大嗰啲 求其搵嘢敲佢有節奏嘅)打拍子 就會將一堆散兵游勇聚合成一個群體<br />\n以往慣例邊個大聲公喇叭就死邊個， 二來呢啲設備貴<br />\n但係水樽就可以有好多個 水樽買得起<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外大家小心雙眼，戴眼罩被人噴油漆就喪失視力，唔戴又會比人插眼<br />\n<br />\n大家亦小心近距離突然由下巴向上大力推有機會導致頸椎受傷 請各位注意安全免生危險<br />\n<br />\n請廣傳<br />\n<br />\n希望無論大家去邊，甚至返工，不了<br />\n都想大家連日常生活都黑衫黑褲口罩笠帽加黑鞋<br />\n令到平時條街見到全黑既人唔再係特徵反而係大多數<br />\n最好個個用現金，咁買飛個個就唔係做突出個一個<br />\n<br />\n全民 BLACK BLOCK<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1203119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1203119</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dGpMPbK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdGpMPbK.png&h=fb4c0fca&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}